{
  "name": "Broom of Cleaning",
  "meta": "[Wondrous Item, uncommon](https://www.dndbeyond.com/magic-items/7472215-broom-of-cleaning)",
  "desc": "This wooden broom, with a sigil of a copper A is made from the Arter factories in the Scaling realm.\n\nMade to clean any room, dishes, clothes and anything that might need a cleaning.\n\nAs you obtain this Broom you can decide what the command word is for it to activate and as an action on your turn you can say its command word for it to begin cleaning the current room, the size of the room does not matter as it cleans it all in 1 minute, folding and putting any clothes and objects on the floor in their respective places.\n\nYou may set a timer in the Broom for it to clean a certain room at a certain time.\n\nIt cannot clean any magical surfaces as a wall of Force."
}